COMMENTARY ON IMPROVING THE IMAGE OF THE SPECIAL LIBRARY.
     
COMMENTS ON PREVIOUS ARTICLES IN 2SPEC. LIBR.1 BY CHARLES BAUER AND W.D.
ROBERTSON (2SEE1 81/2152 AND 81/1157) REGARDING THE MOST IMPORTANT ROLE OF THE
SPECIAL LIBRARY. ARGUES THAT SPECIAL LIBRARIANS SHOULD BECOME INVOLVED IN
EDUCATING HIGH SCHOOL CHILDREN AS TO WHAT CAN BE EXPECTED OF AN EFFECTIVE
SPECIAL LIBRARY.
